high_descs: Turn right, go forward to the stove and face the stove.
Pick up the skillet from the right front burner.
Turn to face the opposite direction, cross the room, then turn left to face the fridge.
Put the skillet on the top fridge shelf, close the fridge door, then take the skillet back out and close the door again.
Turn to your left and cross the room, back to the stove.
Place the skillet back on the right front burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold skillet on a stove burner.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around and bring the pan to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Take the pan out of the fridge and bring it to the stove on the left.
Put the pan back on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around to the right and walk over to the stove.
Pick up the skillet from the front, right burner.
Turn around to the right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the skillet inside, close the refrigerator, open the refrigerator, and close the refrigerator.
Turn around to the left and walk over to the stove.
Place the skillet on the stove burner.
anns.task_desc: Cooling a skillet in the refrigerator.
